      <title>韩国因朝鲜威胁提高外交警戒级别</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/south-korea-raises-diplomatic-alert-levels-citing-north-korea-threats-2024-05-02/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[韩国外交部周四提高了该地区五个外交机构的恐怖主义警戒级别，理由是有情报显示朝鲜可能试图伤害其官员。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/south-korea-raises-diplomatic-alert-levels-citing-north-korea-threats-2024-05-02/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 02 May 2024 09:21:51 GMT</pubDate>
