      <title>菲律宾因南海争端召见中国外交官</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-summons-chinese-diplomat-over-south-china-sea-flare-up-2024-05-02/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[菲律宾周四召见一名中国外交官，抗议北京在南海争议浅滩对菲律宾船只使用高压水枪，称其为骚扰和“危险举动”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-summons-chinese-diplomat-over-south-china-sea-flare-up-2024-05-02/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 02 May 2024 04:22:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>香港央行维持关键利率不变，追踪美联储决定</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/hong-kong-central-bank-keeps-key-rate-unchanged-tracks-fed-move-2024-05-02/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[香港金融管理局（金管局）周四将通过隔夜贴现窗口收取的基本利率维持在 5.75% 不变，以追随美联储维持利率稳定的决定。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/hong-kong-central-bank-keeps-key-rate-unchanged-tracks-fed-move-2024-05-02/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 02 May 2024 03:21:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>官方媒体报道，中国南方道路塌陷已造成 48 人死亡</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/road-collapse-southern-china-kills-36-reports-state-media-2024-05-02/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据官方媒体周四报道，中国广东省一高速公路路段塌方导致车辆滚下斜坡，死亡人数已上升至 48 人，救援工作因泥石流而受阻。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/road-collapse-southern-china-kills-36-reports-state-media-2024-05-02/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 02 May 2024 03:20:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
